data.description: Welcome to your new home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence on over half an acre is the epitome of move-in ready. Step into the bright and airy living spaces, enhanced by brand-new windows that flood the home with natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, providing a welcoming atmosphere for daily living and entertaining guests. This home boasts three spacious bedrooms, each offering a retreat of comfort and relaxation. The freshly stained decks beckon you to unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings, while the meticulously maintained garden adds a touch of natural beauty to the outdoor space. With over half an acre of land, there's ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply basking in the tranquility of your private sanctuary. A standout feature of this property is the detached garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space. Call your favorite Realtor today to schedule a showing!
